        {
          "id": "R02",
          "name": "R02 The Warden's Descent",
          "state": "unexplored",
          "tags": [
            "empty",
            "stairs_down"
          ],
          "reaction_required": false,
          "notes": "Western stairwell to Level 2. The dry rot smell comes from collapsed wooden furniture deeper on Level 2 \u2014 not an active threat. Stairs are structurally sound. DC 13 Perception on the way down reveals faint scratch marks at ankle height \u2014 old tripwire anchors, long stripped of their mechanisms.",
          "encounter_ref": null,
          "treasure_tier": null,
          "box_text": "A narrow room, bare stone, with a single torch bracket long empty. The floor is gritty with blown sand. Stairs cut into the far wall descend steeply into darkness. The air from below is cooler and carries the faint smell of dry rot.",
          "encounter_text": "",
          "treasure_text": "",
          "special_text": "",
          "statblocks": "",
          "image_region": {
            "kind": "rect",
            "x": 210,
            "y": 1474,
            "width": 1474,
            "height": 1868
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "R03",
          "name": "R03 The Drill Chamber",
          "state": "unexplored",
          "tags": [
            "encounter"
          ],
          "reaction_required": false,
          "notes": "Former physical training room for cult initiates. Stone pegs were for climbing drills, floor scoring from blade practice. Skeletons are bound initiates \u2014 a cult death rite. No monetary treasure. Each skeleton wears a corroded bronze ring bearing a crescent moon and dagger \u2014 the cult's sigil. Worthless monetarily but a lore clue worth keeping.",
          "encounter_ref": null,
          "treasure_tier": null,
          "box_text": "A long rectangular room with a low ceiling. Stone pegs protrude from the walls at irregular intervals \u2014 handholds, or obstacles. The floor is scored with countless shallow cuts. Three figures stand motionless against the far wall, wrapped in the remnants of dark linen, their heads bowed.",
          "encounter_text": "3 Skeletons (MM p.272). Unaware \u2014 standing dormant in niches along the north wall. They animate as a group the moment any living creature crosses the midpoint of the room. Fight to the death, will not pursue beyond room exits. They spread to flank using the room's width. Stone pegs on the walls count as difficult terrain near the walls.",
          "treasure_text": "",
          "special_text": "",
          "statblocks": "### Skeleton\n\n_Medium undead, lawful evil_\n\n- **Armor Class** 13 (armor scraps)\n- **Hit Points** 13 (2d8 + 4)\n- **Speed** 30 ft.\n\n|                  |   Str. |   Dex. |   Con. |   Int. |   Wis. |   Cha. |\n|------------------|--------|--------|--------|--------|--------|--------|\n| **Score**        |     10 |     14 |     15 |      6 |      8 |      5 |\n| **Modifier**     |     +0 |     +2 |     +2 |     -2 |     -1 |     -3 |\n| **Saving Throw** |     +0 |     +2 |     +2 |     -2 |     -1 |     -3 |\n\n- **Damage Vulnerabilities** bludgeoning\n- **Damage Immunities** poison\n- **Condition Immunities** exhaustion, poisoned\n- **Senses** darkvision 60 ft., passive Perception 9\n- **Languages** understands all languages it knew in life but can't speak\n- **Challenge** 1/4 (50 XP)\n\n#### Actions\n\n_**Shortsword.**_ _Melee Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 5 (1d6 + 2) piercing damage.\n\n_**Shortbow.**_ _Ranged Weapon Attack:_ +4 to hit, range 80/320 ft., one target. _Hit:_ 5 (1d6 + 2) piercing damage.",
          "image_region": {
            "kind": "rect",
            "x": 1342,
            "y": 3000,
            "width": 1302,
            "height": 1511
          }
        },
